<a href="https://coveralls.io/github/markdown-it/markdown-it?branch=master" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://coveralls.io/repos/markdown-it/markdown-it/badge.svg?branch=master&amp;service=github" alt="Coverage Status"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a>
